    - [Thread_join_code_co_name_eq_join,
       Thread.join.__code__.co_name.__eq__,
       ["join"],
       true,
       "threading.Thread.join.__code__.co_name.__eq__('join') == True — Thread.join is a pure-Python method defined in Lib/threading.py; its code object's co_name attribute records the method name 'join' (4 chars); str.__eq__('join') returns True; no prior threading spec checks Thread.join.__code__.co_name via thrdmore79; new to extra79"]
